  "title": "Simple Shops",
  "description": "Adds player shops",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px;\">\n    <table style=\"text-align: center; margin: auto;\">\n        <tbody>\n            <!-- BODY START -->\n            <tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"https://wolforcept.github.io/images/simpleshops_stockupdate.png\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1070\"/></p></td></tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"https://wolforcept.github.io/images/simpleshops2.png\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1070\"/></p></td></tr>\n<tr>\n    <td colspan=\"2\">\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><strong>Simple Shops Mod</strong></span></p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">This mod adds Player Shops and Creative Shops</span></p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">that are very easy to set up and use!</span></p>\n        <p>&nbsp;</p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Simply craft the shop and place it on the ground.</span></p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Right click</strong> with an item to <strong>set the price</strong>,</span></p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">and <strong>right click again</strong> to insert some <strong>items to sell</strong>.</span></p>\n        <p>&nbsp;</p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">You can leave it anywhere, since no other player can break it!</span></p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">You can <strong>collect your profits</strong> afterwards with <strong>left click</strong>.</span></p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">If you wish to <strong>break your shop</strong>, you can do it with<strong> left click while sneaking</strong>.</span></p>\n        <p></p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Update! Now you can add a Stock Viewer to your shop! With customizable colours too!</span></p>\n        <p></p>\n        <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Check the tutorial video below!</span></p>\n         <p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><a>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yb0MZE6b5Fk</a></span></p>\n       <p></p>\n        \n    </td>\n</tr>\n            <!-- BODY END -->\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <br />\n    <hr /><br />\n    <!--  -->\n    <!--  -->\n    <!--  -->\n    <table style=\"text-align: center; margin: auto;\">\n        <tbody>\n            <!-- DISCORD LOGO -->\n            <tr>\n                <td>\n                    <img src=\"https://wolforcept.github.io/images/line.png\" />\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><a href=\"https://discord.gg/prpWgGu\"><img\n                                    src=\"https://wolforcept.github.io/images/discord650x366.png\" width=\"650\"\n                                    height=\"200\" /></a><br /></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Feel free to join the discord and share\n                        your ideas and feedback!</span><br /><br /></td>\n            </tr>\n            <!-- BISECT HOSTING LOGO -->\n            <tr>\n                <td><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/wolforce\"> <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/logos/dark_text@1538x500.png\" alt=\"\"\n                            width=\"650\" height=\"211\" /></a><br />Sponsored by BISECT HOSTING<br />Dedicated to make your Minecraft server hosting\n                    experience as easy and affordable as it can possibly be.<br />Get 25% off your first month for any gaming server with the code\n                    \"<strong>wolforce</strong>\".<br /><br /></td>\n            </tr>\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <br />\n    <hr /><br />\n    <!--  -->\n    <!--  -->\n    <!-- BOTTOM TABLE -->\n    <!--  -->\n    <!--  -->\n    <table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; display: inline;\">\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td>&nbsp;</td>\n                <td>&nbsp;</td>\n                <td><a style=\"color: #17a12e; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/mi